me</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6i-1dqrxc-026\"><strong>Description</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6j-taf17e-027\"><strong>Link to document</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6j-vph7rx-028\">Jenius Pay - Xendit Manual Tracker</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mmk40g6j-ra53ew-029\"><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6j-yqzydw-030\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb2-08t5r8-066\">Sales to Fill the date, BID and merchant name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6j-49d57m-031\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb2-w2wlf1-067\">MO would be fulfilled</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmk40g6j-4zcqbo-032\"><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6j-2nwumv-033\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb2-q9bmoh-068\">Company Name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6j-r3wbhh-034\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb2-cs5wfr-069\">Date of Establishment</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6j-5conn6-035\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb2-ihakct-070\">Website</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6j-vrfxlw-036\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb2-kpvbin-071\">Business Type</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6j-um0rog-037\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb3-035yfu-072\">Merchant’s email</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6j-qfdmrd-038\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb3-oacvit-073\">NPWP</p></li></ul></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6k-wthrqb-039\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/u/0/d/1iFdRE6XiiXRtnY4-Sz6einaHgQQuGAnqzSvD0FqPveQ/edit\"><u>[ACTIVE] JeniusPay Manual Activation Tracker</u></a></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6k-7no7fq-040\">Jenius Pay - Xendit Bulk Activation Form</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6k-el0jrv-041\">Jenius Pay form that need submit to Jenius Pay via email. </p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6k-5cdaok-042\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spre