Jenius Pay Flow</h2><h2 data-block-id=\"mmk49aek-c3apef-192\"><img data-block-id=\"mmk40g6n-wznxyy-059\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-jenius-pay-image-ohz5bkc2.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></h2><h2 data-block-id=\"mmk49aek-nzhcrs-193\"><a id=\"_ozyaieexd4q6\" display=\"false\"></a>Merchant Requirements </h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6n-cisx94-061\"><strong>Category</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6n-4in8ll-062\"><strong>Requirement</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6n-tota8x-063\">Individual</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mmk40g6n-oty2yk-064\"><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6n-9wv92n-065\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb6-7z8hkr-074\">Xendit NPWP Number</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6n-cgadet-066\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb6-181pph-075\">Date of Establishment</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6n-qcen8q-067\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb6-a91zcp-076\">Website</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6o-g83upv-068\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb6-l1obhd-077\">Business Email</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6o-o2n3o7-069\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb6-qw2lc2-078\">Company Name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6o-oar9jr-070\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb6-b0o6ay-079\">Logo</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6o-abuce7-071\">Entity</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mmk40g6o-tlfqmf-072\"><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6o-logb7l-073\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb6-5gr6dc-080\">NPWP Company Number</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6o-18j0xs-074\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb6-7m3yjq-081\">Date of Establishment</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6o-ush65c-075\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb6-6yvycs-082\">Website</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6o-88a8o3-076\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb6-t3e9d6-083\">Business Email</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6o-woro4e-077\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb6-8mmzf5-084\">Company Name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6o-yb72jp-078\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb6-9s9w2l-085\">Logo</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6o-lvfobe-079\">Restricted Business</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mmk40g6o-9q531o-080\"><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6o-s8ny3t-081\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb6-jtumg4-086\">Not have restricted business as long as merchant already pass MO KYC</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6p-guay1p-082\">Website Requirements</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mmk40g6p-r405yb-083\"><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6p-ya43zr-084\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvb7-cws2wa-087\">Not have website requirements as long as pass MO BDD KYC</p></li></ul></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mmk40g6p-0kervl-085\"><a id=\"_fp25cegffkwe\" display=\"false\"></a>Activation SLA</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6p-9uud0u-086\"><strong>Tech and Settlement Mode</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6p-4yuuwz-087\"><strong>SLA</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6p-c2b4h9-088\">Aggregator</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6q-wy7k8m-089\">Submit to Jenius Pay = every friday</p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6q-nycaq5-090\">Jenius Pay to review merchant application = 3-5 working days</p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6q-e0n1vh-091\">Xendit to activate = every thursday by Digipay team</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mmk40g6q-tnefvd-092\"><a id=\"_uws4fq6qohge\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mmk40g6q-7r8tvv-093\"><a id=\"_tldpiteqz7pm\" display=\"false\"></a>Onboarding Steps</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6q-utugcb-094\">Category</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6q-y9842c-095\">No</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6q-91xrpq-096\">Steps</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6q-l022dp-097\">owner</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6q-arg62c-098\">Merchant applies to Xendit</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6r-9wrim8-099\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6r-vwwydt-100\">Merchant applies for an account with Xendit, and needs to pass KYC.</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6r-dr4vph-101\">Merchant</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6r-e3rwly-102\">Merchant requests for Jenius Pay activation</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6r-krnako-103\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6r-d13p18-104\">CS/AM Inbound Sales will fill out the merchant details on <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1W_GNmPPGzlDjooiZcLfi_76kJpuWez_jexANunghyCs/edit#gid=0\"><u>Jenius Pay Manual Activation Tracker</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6s-j8ear3-105\">CS/AM Inbound</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6s-6yhlix-106\">MO Fill Out In Jenius Pay Tracker</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6s-3zt1ja-107\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6s-nyr3td-108\">MO also fulfilled the blank details in the Jenius Pay tracker for column <strong>E</strong>, <strong>F</strong>, <strong>G</strong>, <strong>H</strong>, <strong>M</strong> dan <strong>P</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6s-lu6301-109\"><strong><img data-block-id=\"mmk40g6s-8xhu5f-110\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-jenius-pay-image-quihyr59.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6s-t0yoja-111\"><strong><img data-block-id=\"mmk40g6s-4mhyxu-112\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-jenius-pay-image-j0p3hxoz.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6s-5p3hr1-113\"><strong><img data-block-id=\"mmk40g6s-qsqwca-114\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-jenius-pay-image-lvyj5j1e.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6s-698t6x-115\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6t-0izwa5-116\">MO fill out the Jenius Pay Bulk Registration Form</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6t-w4uuyw-117\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6t-pe1qyf-118\">After MO fulfilled the details in tracker, MO move the details to the <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ctcz29jLWFtphaoVBXg4ns_UF1d0vunT/edit#gid=53244091\"><u>Bulk Registration Form Jenius Pay</u></a></p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6t-sli7hn-119\"><img data-block-id=\"mmk40g6t-v29vsu-120\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-jenius-pay-image-c86ai9m8.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6t-02vw8i-121\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6t-39ojks-122\">MO send submission via email</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6t-r7rjpu-123\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6t-500ibn-124\">MO will send the submission every <strong>friday</strong> via email with details :<br type=\"inline\"><br type=\"inline\"><strong>Subject</strong> : [merchantops] [Onboarding] Submission Jenius Pay (<strong>Submission Date</strong>) - Batch (<strong>Number</strong>)</p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-9cvm1o-127\"><strong>Body email</strong> :<br type=\"inline\"><br type=\"inline\">Dear Jenius Pay Team,</p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-v8t2pf-130\">Berikut kami informasikan merchant yang akan mendaftar Jenius Pay pada:</p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-p6hbtx-131\">Hari : (<strong>Submission date</strong>)</p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-8aukax-132\">Jumlah merchant : (<strong>total merchant submitted</strong>)</p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-ou5r29-133\">Formulir terlampir.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-31gmq6-134\">Demikian yang dapat kami sampaikan. Terima kasih atas perhatian dan kerjasamanya.</p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-435fmz-135\"><img data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-1wgwac-136\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-jenius-pay-image-40kt25nl.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-5qunlr-137\">Attached file :</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-m2khl7-138\"><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-6elxeo-139\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvbb-wmnoh9-088\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/u/0/d/1ctcz29jLWFtphaoVBXg4ns_UF1d0vunT/edit\"><u>Bulk Registration Form Jenius Pay V1.0.xlsx</u></a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-5ucxen-140\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvbb-w0c99r-089\">Merchant Logo</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-acryk4-141\"><img data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-fxse4x-142\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-jenius-pay-image-cz6al993.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6u-lvyg3u-143\"><strong>Sending to</strong> : <a><u>DITTA.WIJAYANI@btpn.comlidon.sianturi@btpn.comjenius.partnership@btpn.com</u></a></p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6v-pyamy8-144\"><strong>Cc</strong> : <a><u>Julie GuTommy Bongmerchantops@xendit.co</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6v-a63r11-145\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6v-tntp3h-146\">MO updated to Jenius Pay tracker</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6v-nyxpm7-147\">6</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6v-x7xog5-148\">After email, MO will update the sheet in column <strong>R, S </strong>and<strong> T</strong> for:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mmk40g6v-om6b4o-149\"><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6v-oun545-150\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvbc-bw3j1c-090\">notify whether already submitted as submission or not</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6v-900yww-151\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvbc-duakc4-091\">Submitted date</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mmk40g6v-rx9fnu-152\"><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvbc-zz2rt3-092\">latest batch are sent</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6v-x149ga-153\"><img data-block-id=\"mmk40g6v-2s1iom-154\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-jenius-pay-image-ral9mx2s.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6w-k10n84-155\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6w-s7opxa-156\">Feedback from Jenius Pay</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6w-jv5d41-157\">7</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6w-69444z-158\">Jenius Pay would be give Xendit the feedback to MO and notify that merchant already got the Merchant ID/credentials</p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6w-us3nfu-159\"><img data-block-id=\"mmk40g6w-j2f8up-160\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-jenius-pay-image-00jqdhbq.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6w-h2bked-161\">Partner</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6w-smstzq-162\">MO will check the feedback</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6w-x8fr52-163\">8</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6x-vu5ix3-164\">MO check the feedback from Jenius Pay via Excel sheet on Merchant ID in column <strong>O</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6x-hdr9ku-165\"><strong><img data-block-id=\"mmk40g6x-o6hk20-166\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-jenius-pay-image-pqlnkedl.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6x-z7crym-167\"><img data-block-id=\"mmk40g6x-jgdbbl-168\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-jenius-pay-image-5h8ny2ac.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6x-60moq4-169\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6x-owgi6x-170\">MO input the Merchant ID in tracker</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6x-xp65m8-171\">9</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6x-p84eew-172\">MO input the Merchant ID column <strong>O </strong>in JeniusPay tracker on column <strong>S</strong> and the date provided Merchant ID from Jenius Pay on column <strong>T</strong></p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6x-k3grh2-173\"><strong><img data-block-id=\"mmk40g6x-14xyw1-174\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-jenius-pay-image-c5ibo58y.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6x-dmgoi5-175\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6y-ws91ph-176\">Digipay will activate from their side</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6y-iyhqtx-177\">10</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6y-049sxj-178\">Digipay team will take a look the tracker every <strong>thursday</strong> and use the Merchant ID that MO already input to activate the merchant Jenius Pay by manually from their side</p><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6y-b1kd38-179\"><img data-block-id=\"mmk40g6y-7p6y2p-180\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/copy-of-sop-jenius-pay-image-dfh67nlp.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mmk40g6y-lxavq1-181\">Digipay</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mn5kpvbf-1xjgk8-093\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Jenius Pay","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"JeniusPay","Slug":"jeniuspay-1","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"JeniusPay","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"JeniusPay","Slug":"jeniuspay-1","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"JeniusPay","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"JeniusPay","Slug":"jeniuspay-1","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"JeniusPay","Description":null}]